<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Changed Successfully</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div>
        <div>
            <h1>Password Changed Successfully</h1>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p>This email confirms that the password for your account has been successfully changed.</p>
            <p>If you made this change, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
            <p>
                You can now log in with your new password:
                <a href="<%= loginUrl %>">Login to Your Account</a>
            </p>
            <p>If you did not request this password change, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
            <p>Thank you,<br>The Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
